      <h1 class="mt-4 mb-4">FAQ - Student Square</h1>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="mb-3">1. What is Student Square?</h3>
        <p>
          Student Square is an educational platform dedicated to student
          counselling and social development. We provide a range of services and
          resources to support students in their academic journey and personal
          growth.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="mb-3">2. What services does Student Square offer?</h3>
        <p>
          Student Square offers a variety of services including student
          counseling, career guidance, school visiting, academic support,
          mentorship programs, and workshops on various topics such as study
          skills, time management, and stress management.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="mb-3">
          3. How can I be benefited from student counselling?
        </h3>
        <p>
          Student counseling can provide you with a safe and confidential space
          to discuss any challenges you may be facing, whether academic,
          personal, or emotional. Our professional counselors are trained to
          help you navigate these difficulties and develop strategies for
          success.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="mb-3">4. Who are the counselors at Student Square?</h3>
        <p>
          Our counselors are qualified professionals with expertise in student
          counseling and psychology. They are dedicated to supporting students
          and helping them overcome obstacles, set goals, and thrive
          academically and personally.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="mb-3">5. How do I schedule a counselling session?</h3>
        <p>
          For scheduling a counselling session, simply visit our website and
          navigate to the counselling section. There, you'll find instructions
          on how to book an appointment. We offer both in-person and virtual
          counseling options for your convenience.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="mb-3">
          6. Can Student Square help me with career guidance?
        </h3>
        <p>
          Absolutely! We understand that choosing a career path can be
          overwhelming. Our career guidance services are designed to assist you
          in exploring different career options, identifying your strengths and
          interests, and making informed decisions about your future.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="mb-3">
          7. Are there resources available for academic support?
        </h3>
        <p>
          Yes, we do provide a range of resources for academic support,
          including study materials, competitive exam preparation guidelines,
          time management techniques, and effective learning strategies. These
          resources are designed to help you improve your academic performance
          and reach your full potential.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="mb-3">8. Are there any mentorship programs available?</h3>
        <p>
          Yes, we do offer mentorship programs where experienced professionals
          from various fields provide guidance and support to students. These
          programs aim to foster personal and professional development, helping
          you gain valuable insights and build networks within your desired
          field.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="mb-3">9. Are the workshops and seminars free?</h3>
        <p>
          Some of our workshops and seminars may be free of charge, while others
          may have a nominal fee. The pricing details for each event will be
          mentioned on our website or during the registration process. We strive
          to offer affordable and accessible resources to students.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="mb-3">
          10. Are there any fees associated with using Student Square?
        </h3>
        <p>
          Student Square offers both free and paid services. Basic features and
          resources are available for free to all users. However, certain
          specialized counseling services or advanced features may require a
          fee. The pricing details for such services are provided on the
          website.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="mb-3">
          11. How can I stay updated with Student Square's offerings and events?
        </h3>
        <p>
          To stay updated, you can subscribe to our newsletter, follow our
          social media accounts, or regularly visit our website. We frequently
          update our platforms with the latest information on workshops,
          counseling services, and other student-centered initiatives.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="mb-3">
          12. How can I contact the Student Square support team?
        </h3>
        <p>
          For any queries or assistance, you can reach out to the Student Square
          support team by visiting the "Contact Us" page on the website. They
          will respond to your inquiry promptly and provide the necessary
          support.
        </p>
      </div>

